{"id": "1348917354146562068", "channel_id": "1348612101081534535", "type": 0, "author_id": "239474863570419712", "author_name": "applepieeater123", "author_bot": false, "content": "Hello, I wanted to ask for clarification on the【投稿內容】section of the original post, does the submitted artwork need to contain elements related to the events and content of the most recently-released story chapter, or simply just include anything that's currently implemented in the game (for example, upcoming revealed awakeners not-yet implemented would be content that's off-limits, but other characters would be ok)? Also, would it be possible to release a simple translation of the questions on the submission query page linked? The text on the quiz cannot be copied to be inserted into machine translation software so it's difficult for overseas players. \n\n您好，我想請您澄清一下原帖中的【投稿內容】部分，投稿作品是否需要包含與最近發佈的故事章節的事件和內容相關的元素，還是只要包含目前遊戲中已實作的任何內容即可（例如，即將揭曉但尚未實作的覺醒者將是禁止投稿的內容，但其他角色則可以）？另外，是否有可能將連結到提交問卷頁面上的問題做一個簡單的翻譯？測驗上的文字無法複製到機器翻譯軟體中，所以對海外玩家來說很困難。 (本部分為機器翻譯，閱讀時若有任何不便，敬請見諒)", "timestamp": "2025-03-11T07:15:58.901000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1348612101081534535", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "【結束|Finish】🎨獎勵升級🎨彌薩格大學『毀損灰霧之都』二創活動開啟，限定頭像框、無門檻參與獎等你來拿！", "forum_channel_id": "1181135756958371881"}
